    "start": 3328534.0,
    "end": 3348775.0,
    "text": "Just to build on the last point on the education component of it, what is the thinking and planning around continuing and perhaps even enhancing the education underway right now between now and the time that we actually take action on this? Are you contemplating anything in particular?"
