    "start": 4176730.0,
    "end": 4189826.0,
    "text": "Um, this just seems like a no-brainer to me. Um, peace and quiet in your own house seems pretty basic. Right now, I don't know the exact hours— is it 7 to 11 or 7 to 10?"
