    "text": "Sorry, your comment just made me think of something. Um, to that point, I think it's important that we communicate that to the public as far as we have this, this piece of equipment, we have this asset that requires maintenance. This is the deal, this is what it's going to cost over time. You're going to see this go up naturally. This is something that we cannot we're limited on what we can do. So I think just communicating that effectively and consistently to our community would, would go a long way. Thank you."
