    "text": "Sure. So, Mayor, Council, we have one more presentation on stormwater utility. From counting the slides, about 14 slides. I'm sure Mr. Ito and Annie can go through them very quickly if Council so chooses. But this is also in conjunction with the FY27 budget to try to give Council and the residents an update of what we're projecting when it comes to any rate increases And am I correct in gauging that the presentations and discussions that follow that will be brief?"
