    "speaker": "Councilmember Tom Peterson",
    "speaker_source": "resolved",
    "speaker_source_detail": "",
    "start": 13412237.0,
    "end": 13442764.0,
    "text": "I agreed and appreciated, but, uh, it's also typically the case that there are design alternatives and options. and at this conceptual phase, it might be helpful for people to understand not just the issue that we are trying to address here, but kind of a full range, at least conceptually, of options. And if in fact there is only one option, that's good to know, but it's usually not the case, and it usually is very helpful for people to see the different potential options that might be considered. Correct."
